title: Week 10 NFL DFS Picks & Advice (Fantasy Football 11/12)
description:
Will Brinson, Heath Cummings and Frank Stampfl link up to offer DFS advice for Week 10 of the NFL season.
Bills-Cardinals (4:00)
Seahawks-Rams (8:30)
Texans-Browns (11:00)
Broncos-Raiders (15:15)
Jaguars-Packers (21:45)
Bucs-Panthers (26:00)
49ers-Saints (29:30)
Chargers-Dolphins (32:45)
Eagles-Giants (36:00)
Bengals-Steelers
Washington-Lions
Beer!
